      "content": "thanks for that. i'm hearing a lot of concern from folks here about whether these costs are actually worth it. some people are saying the benefits are just theoretical and don't really offset the actual damage to local jobs and growth. do you have any data or common arguments that back up the idea that these regs might do more harm than good for small shops?",
